{"tid":367374,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"內向既人同外向既人相處 真係好攰","createTime":"2017-08-20T16:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T16:08:57.000Z","uid":58333,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d79d5a7d7982a3bcf982949c08068dc60489755f","tid":367374,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:40:41.000Z","msg":"如題 小弟毒撚一個 同外向既人相處 真係覺得好chur 好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如自己多數都係單獨行事 咁所有野唔使就黎就去 跟自己schedule就得 好free 時間都好用好多<br />\n而外向既人 就成日乜都話一齊做一齊做咁 好似得自己一個會死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又例如去exchange果陣 自己已經連續出左好多日街玩 終於到星期日 可以抖下<br />\n而有個外向既flatmate到左星期日一大朝8,9點 就問有無人同佢一齊出去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 有無咁怕悶<br />\n<br />\n唔知咁多位內向巴絲打有無同感呢?<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 想問下外向既巴絲:<br />\n點解身邊成日都要有人陪先得? 係咪真係怕悶得好緊要? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以唔好再chur內向既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好辛苦呀"},{"pid":"4da43bab84b6e653aec656214d7e0243655371f9","tid":367374,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:55:37.000Z","msg":"每分每刻都要惗話題 刺激過all in 700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38efedddfe1d966e16d19d948eb80ba5957420ed","tid":367374,"uid":71473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:34:53.000Z","msg":"內向人表示完全理解，真心單獨開心好多"},{"pid":"febbaae656ae9d02d7bc37ebd4a4c03cea3a321f","tid":367374,"uid":26539,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:37:09.000Z","msg":"諗話題真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次聚完一散就感到極度疲倦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h